This repository contains the solutions to the following problems in Assignment-1 for ITP (Fall 2025):
  1.Question1 (Converting a (max 6 digit) number in figures to words)-->num2eng.cpp
  2.Question2 (Arithmetic operations on two fractions, and simplyfying the result)-->Q2.cpp
  3.Question3 (Checking if a given number is a perfect number)-->Q3.cpp
  4.Question4 (Calculating the square root of a given number without using built in functions like sqrt())-->Q4.cpp
  5.Question5 (Printing a pyramid pattern using digits based on an input(n))-->Q5.cpp
